      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting. While mechanically sound, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the paint. Inside, the upholstery exhibits typical wear and tear, including some staining and minor scuffs on the dashboard. It is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
