      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, resulting in a presentation that is indistinguishable from its original showroom state. The exterior finish remains deep and lustrous, while the cabin provides an environment of pristine refinement. Rigorously inspected and mechanically superlative, this offering represents the zenith of its class, intended for the most discerning of clientele who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
