    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' sparkle and a smooth ride, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
