    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully overhauled for optimal phase timing. The chassis integrity is guaranteed via a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring maximum traction. The suspension remains true to factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in the platform is known for. The exterior retains its factory paint depth with no evidence of panel deviation or clear coat failure. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the serious collector.",
